 ### Click mode
 
 The `click` mode simply triggers a click in the middle of the selection area.
+Set `click_count` to `2` or `3` for double or triple clicks:
+
+```sh
+wl-kbptr -o modes=floating,click -o mode_floating.source=detect -o click_count=2
+```
 
